sec.p:
Data were analysed in the R statistical environment (version 3.2.1) using unpaired Student’s t tests to compare strains, doses and time points (Ihaka and Gentleman 1996). p values were false discovery rate corrected (p
adjusted) to adjust for multiple testing (Storey and Tibshirani 2003). ED50 values with 90 % confidence intervals were determined by fitting response curves using a four-parameter log-logistic model (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
